				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/B%E1%BA%A3o-v%C5%A9-1/poem-g6I5L8XHizldPnnDsM18BA">Bảo vũ 1 - 鴇羽 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/Bi-ph%E1%BA%ABn-thi/poem-d-K5myQmQMd-x20ZH01L_w">Bi phẫn thi - 悲憤詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/B%E1%BB%99-xu%E1%BA%A5t-H%E1%BA%A1-M%C3%B4n-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-3-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-YKAyF5mGn9Juk_OLsOQw9A">Bộ xuất Hạ Môn hành kỳ 3 - Đông thập nguyệt - 步出夏門行其一－冬十月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/D%C4%A9nh-Ch%C3%A2u-l%C3%A3o-%C3%B4ng-ca/poem-sMaN29nfwosLLi7BpB4dYg">Dĩnh Châu lão ông ca - 穎州老翁歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/author-0SVWGWsIUnN7yr-6nBm82Q">Nạp Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-L%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8B-gia-ph%E1%BA%A3/poem-6sFEtBYOollOpRmBv1yhpg">Đề Lư thị gia phả - 題盧氏家譜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/%C4%90%E1%BB%87-ng%C5%A9-c%E1%BA%A3nh-Ng%E1%BB%B1-Vi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-tW9euDnQMVSinsJy1G8kEA">Đệ ngũ cảnh - Ngự Viên đắc nguyệt - 第五景－御園得月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-nC6naBeYFtCN3Ft17XDeJw">Thiệu Trị hoàng đế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Kh%C3%AD-ph%E1%BB%A5-thi/poem-A9qWCfFjB1cv4DDTeDhqSA">Khí phụ thi - 棄婦詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BB%91-t%C6%B0-3/poem-qUsiQX-AE9qObIN0cnEmSg">Thố tư 3 - 兔罝 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/T%E1%BB%91ng-bi%E1%BB%87t-Th%C3%B4i-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-t%C3%A1c-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-chinh/poem-3gozSXA1pJAyWCQgbgAgqQ">Tống biệt Thôi trước tác đông chinh - 送別崔著作東征</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-5-V%C5%A9-H%E1%BA%A7u-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-mafM1mCUnuDfKwkIjFwb1Q">Vịnh hoài cổ tích kỳ 5 - Vũ Hầu miếu - 詠懷古跡其五－武侯廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
